description: Updates the specified subscription target in Amazon DataZone.

parameters.name: applicableAssetTypes
parameters.description: The applicable asset types to be updated as part of the UpdateSubscriptionTarget action. (string) ---

parameters.name: authorizedPrincipals
parameters.description: The authorized principals to be updated as part of the UpdateSubscriptionTarget action. (string) ---

parameters.name: domainIdentifier
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon DataZone domain in which a subscription target is to be updated.

parameters.name: environmentIdentifier
parameters.description: The identifier of the environment in which a subscription target is to be updated.

parameters.name: identifier
parameters.description: Identifier of the subscription target that is to be updated.

parameters.name: subscriptionTargetConfig
parameters.description: The configuration to be updated as part of the UpdateSubscriptionTarget action. (dict) --- The details of the subscription target configuration. The content of the subscription target configuration. The form name included in the subscription target configuration.

nested_params.name: formName
nested_params.description: The form name included in the subscription target configuration.
